Mercenary.CharacterBase:OnSelect+f: 49 BB 70 05 AB 73 C7 02 00 00  - mov r11,Mercenary.CharacterBase:IsNpc
Mercenary.CharacterBase:OnSelect+19: 41 FF D3                       - call r11
